Using Repository Pattern

Using TypeScript for backend










FRONTEND

Creating the presentation layer project
npm create vite@latest presentation -- --template react-ts
npm install
npm run dev

Use Redux Toolkit (RTK) for state management
npm install @reduxjs/toolkit
npm install react-redux

Alternatively, I used:
npx degit reduxjs/redux-templates/packages/vite-template-redux presentation
npm install
npm run dev

Store fetched data in Redux Toolkit (RTK) to avoid refetching

Use MUI
npm install @mui/material @emotion/react @emotion/styled

Using roboto
npm install @fontsource/roboto

Installing icons
npm install @mui/icons-material

Added components folder

Testing:
npm install --save-dev @testing-library/react @testing-library/jest-dom @testing-library/user-event jest
npm test
